5 and the record is an Oklahoma single-source record; or
6 3. Records described in paragraph 8, 10, or 11 of subsection A
7 of this section where the record is an Oklahoma single-source
8 record.
9 D. For purposes of seeking an expungement under the provisions
10 of paragraph 10, 11, 12 or 13 of subsection A of this section,
11 offenses arising out of the same transaction or occurrence shall be
12 treated as one conviction and offense.
13 E. D. Records expunged pursuant as a result of a petition filed
