Req. No. 3845 Page 16

1 reco rds. Upon filing of a petition, the court shall set a date for
2 hearing, which hearing may be closed at the discretion of the court,
3 and shall provide thirty (30) days of notice to all interested
4 parties. If, upon hearing, the court determines that there has been
