7 G of Section 18 of Title 22 of the Oklahoma Statutes shall apply to
8 records expunged pursuant to this section.
9 SECTION 5. REPEALER 22 O.S. 2021, Section 18, as last
10 amended by Section 12, Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (22 O.S. Supp. 2025,
11 Section 18), is hereby repealed.
12 SECTION 6. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
13 SECTION 7. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
14 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
15 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
16 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
